            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De locutione et auditione inhonestarum actionum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-d1e114">
               De loqutione et audi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>tione 
               inhonestarum actionum et 
               <lb ed="#O"/>benigna ac placabili loqutione. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>Aspera uel regroa et deuerbis ma<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>lignis 
               ac uiciis. Rubrica. 12 et 13. 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Rd1e120">PSalmista 31 psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Qd1e127">Quorum 
               <cb ed="#O" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#O"/>os male. dictione et amaritudine 
               <lb ed="#O"/>plenum est ueloces pedes eorum 
               <lb ed="#O"/>ad effundendum sanguinem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-d1e141"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Rd1e136">33 
               <lb ed="#O"/>psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Qd1e143">Quis est homo quae uult uitam 
               <lb ed="#O"/>diligit dies uidere bonos. pro<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>hibe 
               linguam tuam a malo et labia 
               <lb ed="#O"/>tua ne loquantur dolum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-d1e154"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Rd1e151">111 psalmus.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Qd1e156">ab auditione mala non timebit 
               <lb ed="#O"/>iustus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-d1e162"> 
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Rd1e161">160. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63588-Qd1e164">Uir linguosus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>non dirigetur in terram. </quote>
               <!--rubric 12 and 13 combined with no header for rubric 13-->
            </p>
         </div>
